title: Video: Louisville takes down Orange
text:
Video from the locker room after Louisville's 88-68 victory over Syracuse on Sunday at the KFC Yum Center Jody Demling 2:21 PM Video from the locker room after Louisville's 88-68 victory over Syracuse on Sunday at the KFC Yum Center 
Here are a few videos from the locker room after Louisville's 88-68 win on Sunday against Syracuse. 
The Cardinals are 23-6 overall and 11-5 in the ACC with two games left to play this season.
